```sql
WITH customer_channel_priority AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
  FROM customer_channels
)
SELECT 
  c.customer_id,
  cc.channel
FROM customers c
LEFT JOIN customer_channel_priority cc
  ON c.customer_id = cc.customer_id AND cc.rn = 1
```

-- revenue_by_channel_city.sql
```sql
WITH customer_channel AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
  FROM customer_channels
),
customer_with_channel AS (
  SELECT 
    c.customer_id,
    cc.channel
  FROM customers c
  LEFT JOIN customer_channel cc
    ON c.customer_id = cc.customer_id AND cc.rn = 1
),
transaction_with_details AS (
  SELECT 
    t.transaction_id,
    t.customer_id,
    t.amount,
    COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown') AS city
  FROM transactions t
  LEFT JOIN stores s
    ON t.store_id = s.store_id
)
SELECT 
  COALESCE(cwc.channel, 'Unattributed') AS channel,
  twd.city,
  SUM(twd.amount) AS total_revenue,
  COUNT(twd.transaction_id) AS transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT twd.customer_id) AS unique_customers
FROM transaction_with_details twd
LEFT JOIN customer_with_channel cwc
  ON twd.customer_id = cwc.customer_id
GROUP BY 
  COALESCE(cwc.channel, 'Unattributed'),
  twd.city
ORDER BY 
  total_revenue DESC,
  channel,
  city
